{"word":"προστατεύω","slug":"προστατεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προστατεύω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:προστατέω'><el>προστατέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be leader</i> or <i>ruler of</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to exercise authority</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>πρ. ὅπως . .</el> , <i>to provide</i> or <i>take care that . .</i> , <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}